                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-44-defend495 t17960406-44-punish261"></join>
               Privately whipped
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before The Right Hon. LORD KENYON.</p>
